From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Jun 2025 00:15:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 04/10] QSDK: DP: wifi: ath12k: Add Rx TLV Filter Configuration
 API's for nrp mode

With the Filter framework, the following APIs are introduced to configure
Rx TLV filters for non associated client (Neighbor-Peer associated to
neighboring AP's).

setup: Configures TLV filters and stores them in the 2D filter array for
       nrp mode.
reset: Clears TLV filters from the 2D filter array for nrp mode.
update: Updates the configured TLV filters to HW using the ring selection
        configuration command.
display: Prints the configured TLV filters.

Patch-dependency:
	0405-0003-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-Rx-TLV-Filter-Configurat.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
